text: Walter Siba,Church of Melanesia Monthly Newsletter December 1976 was the third Anglican Bishop of Ysabel, one of the nine dioceses that make up the Anglican Church of Melanesia. He served from 1995 to 1999.ACOM ==References== Category:Living people Category:Anglican bishops in Oceania Category:20th- century Anglican bishops Category:Bishops of Ysabel Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
